    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "The Debian BTS exposes per-bug machine-readable views via .mbox and structured URLs at bugs.debian.org. Bug reports can also be retrieved in JSON via various community endpoints. The historical SOAP API at bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/soap.cgi is documented for reference.",
